uk.ac.kent.models.records

Class BaseRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.kent.models.records.BaseRecord
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnnualReviewRecord, EmploymentDetailsRecord, PersonalDetailsRecord, ProbationRecord, PromotionRecord, SalaryIncreaseRecord, TerminationRecord

    @MappedSuperclass
public abstract class BaseRecord
extends Object
    Base record is the superclass for all types of records kept in the system.

    It equips all subclasses with basic fields and getters / setters.

    Author:
    norbert
